{"tid":1025421,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"京阪Pre wedding 之旅,求景點(情侶)","createTime":"2019-02-17T10:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T16:04:19.000Z","uid":197096,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ca6bd5d85a89eb31dab785ec7ff1fcb9a0f34d40","tid":1025421,"uid":197096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T10:35:34.000Z","msg":"京阪去左3次,, 正路既去過哂, 如果唔係婚照公司個期係京都影櫻花都唔會去,<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以介紹啲岩情人既景點,? 都係櫻花期,有冇咩地方睇櫻花正?<br />\n呢家主要3日訓大阪,2日訓京都, 奈良,同神戶不考慮<br />\n<br />\n已去過既熱到PK既景點: 萬博,大阪城,神戶,有馬,奈良, 二條城,清水寺一帶,金閣寺,等等....<br />\n<br />\n反而嵐山一帶未去過,今次會去<br />\n暫時諗住去冷啲啲既貴船神社,仁和寺, 租架電單車, 市中心揸上去<br />\n<br />\nPS:屌4月花期京都酒店貴到仆街,800蚊都係住棺材位, 好彩BOOK得早都要1500蚊一晚,<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6d581345dab2aecc7d93b7f4f5fb40d7f6e0c4","tid":1025421,"uid":91813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:32:03.000Z","msg":"飛田新地"},{"pid":"4203cba3e167c24abb6da517af590333c270c402","tid":1025421,"uid":81977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:43:13.000Z","msg":"宇治"},{"pid":"3019d0b6ca54c454642871c4fac9d044544d842a","tid":1025421,"uid":89227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e6d581345dab2aecc7d93b7f4f5fb40d7f6e0c4","tid":1025421,"uid":91813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:32:03.000Z","msg":"飛田新地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:47:18.000Z","msg":"松島新地"},{"pid":"41f3ff8f286d6dfdd0301fc8ab6fabca0f0c25fb","tid":1025421,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:50:38.000Z","msg":"明天我要和昨天的你約會既所有景點"},{"pid":"5256b8e8c49af6a575c3a76cb19569267e92ca6c","tid":1025421,"uid":5218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3e6d581345dab2aecc7d93b7f4f5fb40d7f6e0c4","tid":1025421,"uid":91813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T12:32:03.000Z","msg":"飛田新地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:27:23.000Z","msg":"呢個景正到爆，女既扮雞男既扮嫖客